at.rseiler.spbee.core.annotation

Annotation Type MappingConstructor


  • @Target(value={CONSTRUCTOR,FIELD,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface MappingConstructor
    Indicates which constructor should be used to map the result or the stored procedure.
    • Marks a public constructor in a Entity as mapping constructor. If more than one mapping constructor is used than different names can be used. It's not allowed that two constructors have the same name.
    • Marks a method in a Dao to use the specified mapping constructor.
    • Marks a field in a ResultSet to use the specified mapping constructor.
    Author:
    Reinhard Seiler <rseiler.developer@gmail.com>
